msgctxt "sn15.18:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 15"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 15"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn15.18:0.2"
msgid "2. Dutiyavagga"
msgstr "2. The Second Chapter"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn15.18:0.3"
msgid "18. Puttasutta"
msgstr "18. Son"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.190"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn15.18:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthiyaṃ viharati … pe …"
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

#. </p><p class="added">
msgctxt "sn15.18:1.2"
msgid "“na so, bhikkhave, satto sulabharūpo yo naputtabhūtapubbo … pe …"
msgstr "“It’s not easy to find a sentient being who in all this long time has not previously been your son. …"

msgctxt "sn15.18:1.3"
msgid "alaṃ vimuccitun”ti."
msgstr "This is quite enough for you to become disillusioned, dispassionate, and freed regarding all conditions.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn15.18:1.4"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
